entry.title: Ubuntu安装Nginx
entry.content:
1.下载Nginx

$ sudo apt update

$ sudo apt install nginx

2.调整防火墙

$ sudo ufw app list

没有的话要添加，使“Nginx HTTP”能通过防火墙

$ sudo ufw allow ‘Nginx HTTP’

$ sudo ufw status

3.检查Nginx状态

$ systemctl status nginx

4.输入ip地址出现Nginx的欢迎界面代表安装成功
